nance of the neuron itself is done mainly by the cellular machinery in the neuron.<\/p>\n","answer_id":43542,"question_id":43538,"up_vote_count":3,"last_edit_date":1456094938}],"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/questions/43538/how-much-energy-does-a-neuron-use-for-information-processing-as-opposed-to-just","last_activity_date":1458861176,"creation_date":1456073160,"answer_count":1,"title":"How much energy does a neuron use for information processing as opposed to just surviving?","body":"<p>That is, as part of a neural network in a brain.<\/p>\n","question_id":43538,"tags":["neuroscience","neurophysiology"],"score":3,"accepted_answer_id":43542,"down_vote_count":0,"closed_reason":"too broad","is_answered":true,"view_count":62,"up_vote_count":3,"last_edit_date":1458861176},{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://graph.facebook.com/1518123811849343/picture?type=large","user_type":"registered","user_id":20816,"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/users/20816/%d8%b9%d9%84%db%8c-%d8%a2%d9%81%d8%a7%d9%82","reputation":158,"display_name":"علی آفاق"},"answers":[{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://i.stack.imgur.com/1YczA.jpg?s=128&g=1","user_type":"registered","user_id":9943,"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/users/9943/christiaan","reputation":26721,"display_name":"Christiaan","accept_rate":93},"score":20,"is_accepted":true,"comments":[{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/1e6026c959ce8fb85ba27b90085a54db?s=128&d=identicon&r=PG","user_type":"registered","user_id":16021,"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/users/16021/mindwin","reputation":101,"display_name":"Mindwin"},"score":2,"post_id":44586,"edited":false,"creation_date":1458827329,"comment_id":77733,"body":"Also this is the reason pirates wore eyepatches (to be able to quick switch between sunlit deck and dark rooms inside ships), and why you should keep your eyes shut or stay in a dark room for several minutes before a telescope session."},{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://www.gravata